---
title: Haddock in Garlic Chive Butter with roast potatoes and broccoli
description: The fish in this delicious dish is basted in beautiful lemony garlicy herby butter. These flavours work together to create a sauce that's zesty, rich and fresh all at once.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF200901_R04_W42_UK_R3912-1_MB_Main_high-38689092.jpg
